    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0780b17"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>福州怡山院<persName key="A003636">大安</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0780b18"/><persName key="A003636">釋大安</persName>，姓陳氏，<placeName key="PL000000017166">閩城</placeName>人也。幼年入道，頓拂<lb
ed="T" n="0780b19"/>塵蒙。<date from-iso="0817-01-25" key="j20194882019871" to-iso="0818-02-12">元和十二年</date>，勅建州浦城縣<placeName key="PL000000017141">乾元寺</placeName>置<lb
ed="T" n="0780b20"/>兜率壇，始全戒足。時天雨桂子及地生朱<lb
ed="T" n="0780b21"/>草，刺史<persName key="A010575">元錫</persName>手疏其瑞，上達<ref type="person" target="#A004382">冕旒</ref>。遂迴御<lb
ed="T" n="0780b22"/><anchor xml:id="beg0780002"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0780002"/>，詔改鳳棲寺<!--找不到此地-->號靈感壇焉。<persName key="A003636">安</persName>因往<placeName key="PL000000018628">洪<lb
ed="T" n="0780b23"/>井</placeName>，路出<placeName key="PL000000008820">上元</placeName>，忽逢一老父曰：「<persName key="A003636">子</persName>往<placeName key="PL000000018628">南昌</placeName>，必<lb
ed="T" n="0780b24"/>有所<anchor xml:id="beg0780003"/>得<anchor xml:id="end0780003"/>。」及咨參律學，夜聞二僧談論，遽<lb
ed="T" n="0780b25"/>了三乘之旨，乃以所習付之同人。之<placeName key="PL000000019846">臨川</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0780b26"/>見<placeName key="PL000000019958">石鞏山</placeName><persName key="A010576">慧藏禪師</persName>。<persName key="A010576">藏</persName>之提唱，必持弓弩以<lb
ed="T" n="0780b27"/>擬學人。<persName key="A003636">安</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0780004"/>服<anchor xml:id="end0780004"/>拜未興，唱曰：「看箭。」<persName key="A003636">安</persName>神色<lb
ed="T" n="0780b28"/>不撓，答對不差。<persName key="A010576">石鞏</persName>乃投弩曰：「幾年射，始<lb
ed="T" n="0780b29"/>中半人也矣。」<persName key="A003636">安</persName>遊<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>，入<placeName key="PL000000005248">龍池</placeName>沐浴，雖<pb ed="T" n="0780c" xml:id="T50.2061.0780c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0780c01"/>久寖漣漪，殊無奮暴雨雹之怪，觀者驚悚。<lb
ed="T" n="0780c02"/>後止<placeName key="PL000000028694">溈山</placeName>，禮<persName key="A001984">大圓禪師</persName>，復證前聞而為量<lb
ed="T" n="0780c03"/>果也。時<placeName key="PL000000018603">豫章</placeName>廉使贈太尉<persName key="A010577">崔貞孝公</persName>，則<persName key="A010578">魏公</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0780c04"/>之季父，深契玄機，敦<persName key="A003636">安</persName>之道，飛疏召之，厥<lb
ed="T" n="0780c05"/>譽愈昌。<date from-iso="0873-02-05" key="j20399532040147" to-iso="0873-08-18">咸通十四年</date>，詔宜號<persName key="A003636">延聖大師</persName>，賜<lb
ed="T" n="0780c06"/>紫袈裟一副。<date from-iso="0882-01-27" key="j20432312043614" to-iso="0883-02-14">中和二年</date>示疾，所止法堂巨梁<lb
ed="T" n="0780c07"/>中折。<date key="j20439022043902" when-iso="0883-11-29">三年癸卯十月二十二日</date>，坐化于怡山<lb
ed="T" n="0780c08"/>丈室，春秋九十一，臘六十七。續詔贈<persName key="A003636">圓智大<lb
ed="T" n="0780c09"/>師</persName>，塔號證真。<persName key="A003636">安</persName>不嘗唾地，不處溫房，隨<lb
ed="T" n="0780c10"/>化而衣，天雨而<anchor xml:id="beg0780005"/>浴<anchor xml:id="end0780005"/>。諮法弟子<persName key="A010579">慧長</persName>入<placeName key="PL000000042002">關</placeName>，揚<lb
ed="T" n="0780c11"/><persName key="A003636">安</persName>之德，故有追<app type="cb-app" xml:id="begd1e19627"/>諡<anchor xml:id="endd1e19627"/>也。<placeName key="PL000000002513">博陵</placeName>司空相國仰慕<lb
ed="T" n="0780c12"/>前烈，遂著文頌德。詩人<persName key="A010580">周朴</persName>篤重<persName key="A003636">安</persName>，時入<lb
ed="T" n="0780c13"/>山致禮焉。</p>
